In England, in the seven days to 02 September, there were 179,284 new confirmed cases (317.0 new cases per 100,000). There is no change in cases compared to those confirmed in the previous week (seven days to 26 August). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 07 September is 6,074,040 (10,741 cases per 100,000 population).
